export const SECTIONS = [{"level":2,"title":"STRATEGIC DOSSIER: Tanqueray (Diageo)","content":"\n**A note on method:** This dossier compiles verified findings on Tanqueray, focusing on data corroborated by multiple independent sources. Where a claim is supported by only one source, it is explicitly marked as `[single-source]`. Unverifiable claims, particularly those relying on future-dated publications, have been excluded. All figures are cited with their full source URL inline. The objective is to provide a robust, data-driven foundation for Liquid's strategic recommendations and creative pitches.\n\n---\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"1. History","content":"\nTanqueray gin was founded in **1830** by **Charles Tanqueray** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGeXs7wEfC4Q8GYoe9tDar5hbbJYaWHs35Lzte7SeMMPbuhAS6ybXbI6mg6wk6iJnc0SOPbpDHWEONQbVrh5sxILAhXld1GyBWzOeXV7pcTmAn-1uSRGMh1Gn4mGTn0ZwIUzPqT5ZoIjp1IIELuQ9t49gxkV7c6Nl17vLtZQLAX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHHV06Vsbze3UzcYXJXuQQtbBzAFVl0cmdk40VhHHQKCCKBOtrdy6HlKRRDS-Xa-qiuNwVyzz_YmvrJ4oGuYP7bsTuxM6WFnAn11l5bhwzVg_D9HL0-Cj2KZxttbkC69EPe, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG-dleYbFN7tStMFDhNe1Un0IGh7WvMp3ISqhhqYTEZkj73h_XIwvQcZKE1_g7DZ7FhdctN0Bi0Vmpvfe02K7oVPFq5ijxEZwUjRrRhoe6_2mduLOPc9J8pTaDvpiyVALIMS2C6WIYFrwDzsO41pQGmP9SBN-Jr55omKIon2Z7ZhYHq-0ts10PX0lnhVfr6nqKEOWR1cE8zjwa_59FG]. The initial distillery was established in **Bloomsbury, London, on Vine Street** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGeXs7wEfC4Q8GYoe9tDar5hbbJYaWHs35Lzte7SeMMPbuhAS6ybXbI6mg6wk6iJnc0SOPbpDHWEONQbVrh5sxILAhXld1GyBWzOeXV7pcTmAn-1uSRGMh1Gn4mGTn0ZwIUzPqT5ZoIjp1IIELuQ9t49gxkV7c6Nl17vLtZQLAX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHHV06Vsbze3UzcYXJXuQQtbBzAFVl0cmdk40VhHHQKCCKBOtrdy6HlKRRDS-Xa-qiuNwVyzz_YmvrJ4oGuYP7bsTuxM6WFnAn11l5bhwzVg_D9HL0-Cj2KZxttbkC69EPe]. The original London Dry Gin recipe, utilizing **juniper, coriander seed, angelica root, and liquorice**, has remained **largely unchanged** since its inception [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGeXs7wEfC4Q8GYoe9tDar5hbbJYaWHs35Lzte7SeMMPbuhAS6ybXbI6mg6wk6iJnc0SOPbpDHWEONQbVrh5sxILAhXld1GyBWzOeXV7pcTmAn-1uSRGMh1Gn4mGTn0ZwIUzPqT5ZoIjp1IIELuQ9t49gxkV7c6Nl17vLtZQLAX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHfM1kGYwOD3_WtDSxR084KsGaF73vAdwy5UvbNRAFHCA_u45gLAFW7lV6NQRjyKgGil7rnf-ysXhFp8JlN8AcTewoRna4jtcnYpewAA-7JfEKQIL-v16rB_ATdHcdaqY3wAlLL_fWEoTRrjC02iUAhM18Gflu260hqdnFelOrFOyIM, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHG9ksQlqgdWryVzqUOfE-mF2lKHLAZUTvFKHrDAVLx_jFqpI6vBP5Zw4d_t4MkQ8UYL-oMlSShYJpIGDAoMhsYvRIKZlPV5QkFvJiYY95tp7iaO_KOqjh99W76gf6bydQVSWeRPL_LfVHh]. This precise blend of four botanicals is a hallmark of the classic London Dry style, emphasizing purity and a juniper-forward profile [https://www.diageo.com/en/our-brands/reserve/tanqueray, https://www.tanqueray.com/en-gb/our-story]. In **1898**, Charles Waugh Tanqueray (Charles Tanqueray's son) orchestrated a merger with Alexander Gordon & Co., forming the largest gin house globally [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGeXs7wEfC4Q8GYoe9tDar5hbbJYaWHs35Lzte7SeMMPbuhAS6ybXbI6mg6wk6iJnc0SOPbpDHWEONQbVrh5sxILAhXld1GyBWzOeXV7pcTmAn-1uSRGMh1Gn4mGTn0ZwIUzPqT5ZoIjp1IIELuQ9t49gxkV7c6Nl17vLtZQLAX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHHV06Vsbze3UzcYXJXuQQtbBzAFVl0cmdk40VhHHQKCCKBOtrdy6HlKRRDS-Xa-qiuNwVyzz_YmvrJ4oGuYP7bsTuxM6WFnAn11l5bhwzVg_D9HL0-Cj2KZxttbkC69EPe].\n\n**Botanical Sourcing and Sustainability:** Tanqueray's core botanicals – juniper, coriander seed, angelica root, and liquorice – are fundamental to its consistent flavor profile [https://www.goodygoody.com/products/tanqueray-london-dry-gin, https://www.barsys.com/products/tanqueray-london-dry-gin, https://www.cellarbration.com.sg/blogs/news/the-ultimate-guide-to-tanqueray-gin-unleashing-the-botanical-elegance]. Tanqueray sources **99.9% of its core juniper from Tuscany, Italy** [https://www.diageo.com/en/our-brands/tanqueray/sustainability, https://www.tanqueray.com/en-gb/our-story/botanicals]. Coriander is sourced from regions including **Bulgaria, Russia, Romania, and Albania** [https://www.diageo.com/en/our-brands/tanqueray/sustainability, https://www.tanqueray.com/en-gb/our-story/botanicals].\n\nHowever, the sourcing of these botanicals faces significant vulnerabilities. Climate change, with its unpredictable weather patterns like extended monsoon seasons or droughts, directly impacts botanical yields and quality [https://www.nutraingredients.com/Article/2025/09/10/Climate-change-quality-loss-and-adulteration-Summit-calls-for-sustainable-botanical-supply-chains, https://www.vitafoodsinsights.com/news/botanicals-supply-chain-pressures-create-unsustainable-situation]. For instance, wet harvest years for juniper can reduce the concentration of volatile compounds by approximately **12%**, directly impacting the gin's sensory characteristics [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGPFcFwKDNcbRIGQnPGLB0NPph17ckANp3CZwHpuZ7HO_uoXiV6vDK6E9dENDdvDOeO3_-xV6Nu0iK5GAqsGk8E_S_1HG5Zh5YkydNvrQl-OjfENPE9LAuvAGlkiHj5GNZhYc1PTBAtxYRlIPJDAon6LvvYuJiDTOAS4xglnJKavVk_4xb7pdoE5XftCZO5dvx6Yt4bkpMMpJAAaQ==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGl9fgE5zSeZZ3tAiW6M83bhVJvvCAQOiQHEDNRtxDT5XNFfBd8w19bHT20KI03IWFqvAUlURR_nxWxcrzLbJAcoNAzARGIOg-GSv3rROw0bkgCnI0__flOisHcqUGH6B7DtsYqbqTFlFF5puXy5GjZwkD4pmddVRo==]. Botanical costs have also \"gotten ridiculously expensive over the past few years\" due to staff losses, adverse weather, import fees, and limited supply of exotic or organic ingredients [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHuJ0gIpFxtFG8s52MMprQFsMhMpY8xLQZZE0oQ2wNIAhDJi3OgKOddM2ce9cPxj3GGLbj3An3F8dp4z1VJug2zqYv14ts7Xl8j9A3K5wnWc3Cs0qBjIKXqXzlrHwFUrIzfGtNatN2gpjqj_ksFfzJ2jKC4zz8Gg3MxQLk==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGqpz766b9VEr-2_s8Z-29VmmeTcKvtL0zRk2ydbxjhGs5reX3ceZR_MBUE-XfTUpJp93RFWPtQe-pUt4LnlALI9N0T48CG8L468_iw1XZxOGudALuGcOe_pnRhpHrkdqTiAfOpCyumvEN7K9qoZhCtADWKH4L2ebAaFs1k7h1uJukZohIDCaA==]. Geopolitical instability and trade disruptions in sourcing regions can hinder access to critical ingredients, leading to supply chain delays and increased costs [https://www.arjunanatural.com/top-5-sourcing-challenges-in-plant-based-nutraceuticals/, https://www.redcliff-logistics.com/blog/2026-botanical-sourcing-trends-what-buyers-need-to-know]. Specifically, botanicals sourced from regions like Eastern Europe, Vietnam, India, and Indonesia are particularly susceptible to precarious supply situations and price volatility due to these factors [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGA7p9LOPGZ2qjHrxAz1leA4Pf2OLVOj3Wmo0tIkZYLlxigmn6J3Z1q3FAR8iNfb-_aC2gQRHozUNBd0tb4D5gJtCkdnwbuTPBPFGSDB4AtFSOC-giT41rZfUqn-awUAt2lQKmzEwtYM2Jpw5BEP3XbOBXZBLPVS6eF6tRko6rFe8mceoDl8jM, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFA6bUnuJbkR2lYOg_D5BTU0AvUxYew4aLrABua37cIs6qHih_ZxHwS0mc5rI5osmcG12NkgwNXbXOMkqdWJJlLrjlcIC7g6era3P7ruAjG8JSOjCp7eHHtXPNjWN7rncE1HPexiMH62RrP2rKmNPyvDXrjRSHQZxGZVaYGPyYhW4kgEkKwRjNNFXOTuGITNejGpnVT6BQzPvoDPyVyshw, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFEeViUuyd4JgTal5wpdAV6K7ksEEiaAmQNEBXNMPOHq3LDXHRQ-0tx2PuII2YDOT1RUwVb3M0_422ReWUrhQ1mi9ZngSlVfRPse9NbkOZNgMfoJ0kUYP3iNoKUuamUmrNKZfQXXrRtd9v9lAKrM6G6nKOf0I3UwB65BmP-ahwmIsRb9uHSv6XhBpE9znaw98TVzQ]. Furthermore, unsustainable agricultural practices, often driven by market pressure for low prices, can deplete natural resources and impact biodiversity, particularly for wild-harvested botanicals such as juniper [https://www.jimandtonic.com/blogs/news/crafting-a-sustainable-future-for-gin-discover-the-eco-friendly-practices, https://www.playitgreen.com/blog/sustainable-gin-raise-your-glass-reduce-your-impact]. Addressing these challenges through sustainable sourcing initiatives is becoming increasingly important, as evidenced by competitors like Bombay Sapphire, which aimed to be the first major gin brand made with 100% sustainably-sourced botanicals, achieving this for eight of its ten botanicals by March 2021 [https://www.bacardilimited.com/media/news-releases/bombay-sapphire-on-a-mission-to-be-worlds-most-sustainable-gin/, https://www.sustainablebusinessmagazine.net/bombay-sapphire-on-a-mission-to-be-worlds-most-sustainable-gin/]. Diageo's mitigation strategies for botanical sourcing include sustainable sourcing, regenerative agriculture, diversification, and rigorous quality control, ensuring \"one in 10 botanicals have the quality\" for Tanqueray [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHQwDH9ypf8F0S4ikfkZWbe9xOvwJcR2OMYaM1xQTX8FHzK6BdLiyqWfhjRiSLKnFmdxjkAlCfSuvDWI6DxCnZyHfKVP8-Hc5NVIHwD_WMawwg77XmK9f3UL3L8sPAT8n4pS, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHl85gdH4HZrlD_Oie0WkltwQGk2PoEteolbfBxEwhJ2m6rg7zTr1Yq9nxmQSVGFKRy_z0SRDjFSWHENRb6_1pTHG27foeVynzWVlUcxVCK3pWTugI5mG8qdE1ihBqXGDGzX1Fk4qhxbWJiNwdlNSNi1RhMDQsqyAirv8LG, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGqpz766b9VEr-2_s8Z-29VmmeTcKvtL0zRk2ydbxjhGs5reX3ceZR_MBUE-XfTUpJp93RFWPtQe-pUt4LnlALI9N0T48CG8L468_iw1XZxOGudALuGcOe_pnRhpHrkdqTiAfOpCyumvEN7K_qoZhCtADWKH4L2ebAaFs1k7h1uJukZohIDCaA==]. The specific, quantified financial impact of botanical sourcing vulnerabilities on Tanqueray's profitability is not publicly quantified by Diageo [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF-3qwaWO_PoG6wQKPOJZRu3nt0H5vjbafT6muHWb3mEH1LvcvPU1g0Eu6UTYxzJGSNnzqVj2bzBfAp-YULds8yxy8mRCJTqQVqTk9kr1PO5QAZLokO4Gfo8LVpVNs6aVR-D6Z1sA6P4sXe0FnLYh-yCfvcKHxjl3HX].\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"2. Ownership","content":"\nTanqueray was acquired by The Distillers Company (DCL) in **1922** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFECjw2LPMTLSy5pxzhXACWp1WKPGLScIe2J2Jo3NxO0yWa5AkaC7_BY4t25MPqhrrrVeYq72KEl81V1VWoH9mM0sWO6GStNVv4vV8WgPtfk9U0cr7r4-NbEn69_4NRoJj29CjYJ3fSPpHTxyCu_vKxK6NtBUh0PbsI-DaAWLCJdqtRLRFeA9XmAZL8VAUuC9aViGh5v6qEkzFaLLAp, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHFEEp-tPGKwmLezrfKRryMUJt0UdcmPcFzO1L6SK12hDq3vkovQJfBSeNyUaJG9E5Wk0SQQKDHUUnkqd5zSsQ5wPXtqv_DWj--riEuucek0euKf43Rs6PYeoBr5x7vsk7GVhjfVo4mMQ_7selGdHItJmt1CbreGFmb6Gp81RirxkgH9z8=]. Guinness plc acquired DCL in **1986** for an estimated **£2.6 billion to £4 billion** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFECjw2LPMTLSy5pxzhXACWp1WKPGLScIe2J2Jo3NxO0yWa5AkaC7_BY4t25MPqhrrrVeYq72KEl81V1VWoH9mM0sWO6GStNVv4vV8WgPtfk9U0cr7r4-NbEn69_4NRoJj29CjYJ3fSPpHTxyCu_vKxK6NtBUh0PbsI-DaAWLCJdqtRLRFeA9XmAZL8VAUuC9aViGh5v6qEkzFaLLAp, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEhVe4lg_EOKuQSyUFD9MS1cLlLa7W32PEtFpdebK1GFXgxvDsYywLvfDhvkWtXUS-8nKAR_4X7TX1CXMd4-13-GdL104N-4XJ1A9QxXLBtCV4K3pMarmOQFRaED7JLjA==]. Guinness plc then formed United Distillers in **1987**, bringing Tanqueray under its spirits division [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFECjw2LPMTLSy5pxzhXACWp1WKPGLScIe2J2Jo3NxO0yWa5AkaC7_BY4t25MPqhrrrVeYq72KEl81V1VWoH9mM0sWO6GStNVv4vV8WgPtfk9U0cr7r4-NbEn69_4NRoJj29CjYJ3fSPpHTxyCu_vKxK6NtBUh0PbsI-DaAWLCJdqtRLRFeA9XmAZL8VAUuC9aViGh5v6qEkzFaLLAp, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGdT0rb_5h5URX7PoRltQ6GNrLEXz_y2n8BunknzVM6jKpF7WQPr21LgXwn4GqIYZ-iSYDXTzBPSk60bWdD9DtS5qXj4aHer6LwXyiUAY9eVzcD03Ehu2LheZeszFczXTFxJfMo392YQosV2fvdB7mZbMap4t7UPAUzZaGweGitvoKpTV9eEfDt, https://vertexaisearch.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQElR0BFdVYE0IFwqMtY1o3Gxsz1IspVj6BhkHSpHVg47pOnojyjazJVeqYeP9_dXXf_T-rGafP1F228_LWynRaNrf4Yy2ZK12b9y_SGz-E4XLqPouv6r7jrgp0uX_IdZuxI-oTXpLbRzw==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGh_ctO9S7qmDgGwekMqtShWWCd3qUXnSWbXeDUPoQXL8OkRNmmXs3UGv1f_H1kIm1__yGmEpXrxQjpWoA2L5DM-lQFok6wpmqO3JW-0hCS2Lk9v7pQTs2rmZ04mzzZpfZ1E7waR2QlTNTH, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH9jrKfV3KcZrOlkqBuLloDrpDoB4JMegQINbAHrmTEfQDtIA5IqE-55NUopHHRboBHDmrA_i2aHDaFekQDysG9qE8ZkYgxNRzGi10uweapjEf5wB2G3LBVU5qh1GqyFwdaM-MSh5dEP-_R]. Diageo plc was formed on **December 17, 1997**, through the merger of Guinness plc and Grand Metropolitan plc, valued at **£12 billion ($19 billion)** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFECjw2LPMTLSy5pxzhXACWp1WKPGLScIe2J2Jo3NxO0yWa5AkaC7_BY4t25MPqhrrrVeYq72KEl81V1VWoH9mM0sWO6GStNVv4vV8WgPtfk9U0cr7r4-NbEn69_4NRoJj29CjYJ3fSPpHTxyCu_vKxK6NtBUh0PbsI-DaAWLCJdqtRLRFeA9XmAZL8VAUuC9aViGh5v6qEkzFaLLAp, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEhVe4lg_EOKuQSyUFD9MS1cLlLa7W32PEtFpdebK1GFXgxvDsYywLvfDhvkWtXUS-8nKAR_4X7TX1CXMd4-13-GdL104N-4XJ1A9QxXLBtCV4K3pMarmOQFRaED7JLjA==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFwgoXAnD-MGIExhdxt09w8l7CyJIatKMcRNyV-73GvdPYxT9HX-WVzZKOSr-6LWx99Jhtp1tkVeRjmmp7ia1M60DvAxy9i4wAvuIDQfpgTfUdZJGO6HuX1qcQYlZVoNNy502UQb03-_Rddww==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHhAVmvycQNifk5kdnQvbhsi0ngORgHu9-h4tBATqnuJ-idAqFkIQxaQ-9xdFjf7Od3W-ypE2FWPOt0rGm4cobJsgu24UJUnA44vkiStwC5-NaZ_kd5kMSMzYulkdBIAVwcTeU=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG_O2UJmUnD1vORzZ33oSa8aELVA2aWVWGIKMzRzwiCjKVffPWd3X3YXlUcS1m8_YaHD9212iMm9w3MenGUJlAajoBwHQ1UwyxivAdd2E4xNK7MHtvl6Fud5ZyNQo0uYO0pm9WNmnabdRH00NzW_xZXw==]. Tanqueray is wholly owned by **Diageo plc** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGfF9EGKkMIShodNqw2TZ8gHVwX2SZoA98nLtgM7Fu0SBDUDnbj2N6SoEcuhIADcD35zpyjZnHBXhWiRP_uSWpd613DopSIOCj6_WLGzZK4qyvoUNxaSfMwHSPFpZz9OLal2DiwKm0, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFECjw2LPMTLSy5pxzhXACWp1WKPGLScIe2J2Jo3NxO0yWa5AkaC7_BY4t25MPqhrrrVeYq72KEl81V1VWoH9mM0sWO6GStNVv4vV8WgPtfk9U0cr7r4-NbEn69_4NRoJj29CjYJ3fSPpHTxyCu_vKxK6NtBUh0PbsI-DaAWLCJdqtRLRFeA9XmAZL8VAUuC9aViGh5v6qEkzFaLLAp].\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"3. Positioning","content":"\nTanqueray is positioned as a **leading premium gin globally** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEjvML0Yssx2iuCDHi1zre2i1iLTO_bH1LWED8D3hTIdyBE9h1mvxDyDHsVFpbLrjYFi4H_dnSLggQzmDvk4uJwZ8A2L2GaVG1bepTUE9BIqjW8WV1hJZUOeEaJ8fhOd_bdBjo=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGBK4ygWpSXcg1o_0lzNCfZTxhJIGddNZCZ4O0QLJpbJTbWh5SxmdQoUBhgUsJf1y9KL5RtTjNS5yW_CTl8DfC9KZXsfQzDJlKXNEWxP3hixIzoirXtPgvsWjpEA8F43c37J5l6HTMpoVythsIeQGIt7XWHhGI29DiHIy8=] and is considered one of Diageo's key **'strategic brands'** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEjvML0Yssx2iuCDHi1zre2i1iLTO_bH1LWED8D3hTIdyBE9h1mvxDyDHsVFpbLrjYFi4H_dnSLggQzmDvk4uJwZ8A2L2GaVG1bepTUE9BIqjW8WV1hJZUOeEaJ8fhOd_bdBjo=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEFwLmamNI74zXjw1-oJOQKRpuEZKdchQMsnsP5NY__mmZH_7Vovolt8aMVzCVg_Yccx0AcfVCKZPoDiEf5JFEIuuXSoDjhLIclVGEogtMvbASnes3TP1Chqtjp_KnS2bDGbtp1JELiljmXf953zBHJJAZ-hclL2lux1SXdePX-Edlv9kY=]. Its branding emphasizes **quality and heritage** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQETVqarv5K9D9rN_5zuk0_Q39i76A_wvkAQ7R9WiU51g6NRx9sqPGfaYJB-uXqM5jVhty4vfLuGSKDAqqtSV197Xn1aS9Sh8K1U-DxhNK5687ZdaKHYrKFOa7dIsTrGLeOxQEsUgrSekM2PeHJEDOgGwKYYVZFipvGM1RjP, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFB8f8iYg40Ol5wio6A6F31Ldi5_3gRHXrlrwBSRjapMQ6FlzitFb9KgAgeogrgrzCRg48xE1ZZNcvrmz-im_Gf12XmvN4OgFXfP6zeMyDbNuxXGVzkpollpppfm1Vf4iRCXYkm8cHSdTHd_SDcjN0yqaaoEFzOpgAgwNKNjYUcoA==]. Tanqueray aims to **'elevate the everyday' and bring 'theatre back to gin,'** drawing inspiration from 1920s glamour [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQETVqarv5K9D9rN_5zuk0_Q39i76A_wvkAQ7R7WiU51g6NRx9sqPGfaYJB-uXqM5jVhty4vfLuGSKDAqqtSV197Xn1aS9Sh8K1U-DxhNK5687ZdaKHYrKFOa7dIsTrGLeOxQEsUgrSekM2PeHJEDOgGwKYYVZFipvGM1RjP, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQERdYUlq3Rubbecc2Uavtn_0qwWb-XrtadBPIive6IH1sSMWYPAlCT0YRvn6nIUVaP1mI-BonQovu2OGXFvHOVwyzbL9ij9PxerOeqmybzfTqRJgUKqzkdcIN2_wCMdLXoto3K-5p0aVE8xhfqwBuA6jY6afZySfZ3jxvi7UMuh0Y4f13kwoQt3LhTwmTV66zYB97016otxvJ_yEPKf_g==].\n\nTanqueray's core London Dry Gin typically retails in the **$25-$30 range in the US** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEZOxK4rXtYJHouvNfNNB8YC4uN48HwBOV69xZ9xn9Ep8M5vAV1EpPvmcu2VF2_n_BBAhXnrkn3TlIirylgVLXhZ3PLFU1DiwAGAWTqjR4KSlStqMjAo41CPhLDm5PKgcq-nQwf6P8u0ABKtfAr_bEP38RcWpOYxbl9MgX0xh0KafH9, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEjvML0Yssx2iuCDHi1zre2i1iLTO_bH1LWED8D3hTIdyBE9h1mvxDyDHsVFpbLrjYFi4H_dnSLggQzmDvk4uJwZ8A2L2GaVG1bepTUE9BIqjW8WV1hJZUOeEaJ8fhOd_bdBjo=]. Its super-premium variant, **Tanqueray No. TEN**, launched in **2000** as the first-ever super-premium gin, commands a price point of approximately **$44 in the US** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEZOxK4rXtYJHouvNfNNB8YC4uN48HwBOV69xZ9xn9Ep8M5vAV1EpPvmcu2VF2_n_BBAhXnrkn3TlIirylgVLXhZ3PLFU1DiwAGAWTqjR4KSlStqMjAo41CPhLDm5PKgcq-nQwf6P8u0ABKtfAr_bEP38RcWpOYxbl9MgX0xh0KafH9, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEjvML0Yssx2iuCDHi1zre2i1iLTO_bH1LWED8D8D3hTIdyBE9h1mvxDyDHsVFpbLrjYFi4H_dnSLggQzmDvk4uJwZ8A2L2GaVG1bepTUE9BIqjW8WV1hJZUOeEaJ8fhOd_bdBjo=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFB8f8iYg40Ol5wio6A6F31Ldi5_3gRHXrlrwBSRjapMQ6FlzitFb9KgAgeogrgrzCRg48xE1ZZNcvrmz-im_Gf12XmvN4OgFXfP6zeMyDbNuxXGVzkpollpppfm1Vf4iRCXYkm8cHSdTHd_SDcjN0yqaaoEFzOpgAgwNKNjYUcoA==]. The brand is identified as a **'Ruler' brand**, characterized by a premium or luxury status with an authoritative personality [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQETVqarv5K9D9rN_5zuk0_Q39i76A_wvkAQ7R9WiU51g6NRx9sqPGfaYJB-uXqM5jVhty4vfLuGSKDAqqtSV197Xn1aS9Sh8K1U-DxhNK5687ZdaKHYrKFOa7dIsTrGLeOxQEsUgrSekM2PeHJEDOgGwKYYVZFipvGM1RjP, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQERdYUlq3Rubbecc2Uavtn_0qwWb-XrtadBPIive6IH1sSMWYPAlCT0YRvn6nIUVaP1mI-BonQovu2OGXFvHOVwyzbL9ij9PxerOeqmybzfTqRJgUKqzkdcIN2_wCMdLXoto3K-5p0aVE8xhfqwBuA6jY6afZySfZ3jxvi7UMuh0Y4f13kwoQt3LhTwmTV66zYB97016otxvJ_yEPKf_g==].\n\n**Market Position (Clarified):**\n*   Tanqueray is consistently positioned as the **world's number one premium gin** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFhnmgDo3omIcI-c7KM3xfgEB07znELJYcHEY74Bq72mM5_Rt5vEJc9JqAPjJyjIj28NypHteSHbq3yKWiq6d9HbUWWt3pemn32z7oBH0sfo6ykj-VPmcP0jEqTu4rRA-uHqKhYcKTps5YfLGB4iEcZwPx_O9KCzei-FaLncKvk2g-19e0u1k3zDw==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGlEuUTBBmgMeBfm6cyQBZZTImkIAek0CXc5r7WKYWYxjWsDx6bBiNZdcR21ThC6AQcQ9R_dPxiWis2eGmB6Qtgge7avMFrT11Yw8neUXbK17uFNI4J-HECC8wC6jL66rCS2D6RQVjiq6EMRnaM4wuFCafmu5BlT6v6t0gC9FTtERiy41yqHeZqDECxCz2fupfR]. This claim refers to its strong on-trade dominance and brand equity within the premium segment, rather than overall global volume leadership, which is often skewed by mass-market brands like Ginebra San Miguel (selling over 42 million nine-liter cases in 2024) [https://www.drinksint.com/news/fullstory.php/aid/10041/The_World_s_50_Best_Bars_Brands_Report_2023.html, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2023/01/tanqueray-named-worlds-favourite-gin/, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGA5LklkeLF7AFZeSISzDj3mJ5ZlL_B0_7Pb8gGKS-kBLLBxuodYqeoMCmo4kB9DPEOJHY4OogGa-clTBtRRF_6oLfwCijAuo9Pz6ZHJWYK0Zr9OnBh0WfH_spdul3ealmvKBNqQdYYBCWUaWzbKZ3hqJdusfEAhLj0G8UpZHISu9W7zF0v_wh3A4Ye9cA5D3yNTItuaWF85KwgB9Ky]. The global premium gin market value was **USD 3.72 billion in 2025**, projected to reach **USD 9.43 billion by 2033**, growing at a CAGR of **10.89%** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH8z3miluAd5m32_jEXMczTxZzkRR4_Ej-iUWjFp01uXZ1QreNemKHks7Ir5N9s-FbOwxG_LvktljkyGuzddzzJ1lQBWV2jTxj0KbSeUQVTgBfb50SeD0iJPWCfJf8mzOY8_sra6ZEkt_J9XQNT59fOLWBrVeDYTbRKjasbqst2a-JWbJeVUyIjQ==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGNjfLTp8GGZkkYIEfpYaiwdX7HhjsB1pvzK3M1qoyxwh3YfjmTy380ysATWUnI4CnLNfMA7aJleBqOJR-crJEvnTF-KrKqvR7gZiJQ_x3B0VchIdB-ncz1OlttzcpurVnPwHcof-Vvp0lUkldmW9p7R9qGwaVijEjoQSBBvg==].\n*   In **2024**, Tanqueray was the **second-largest gin brand globally by volume** among leading international brands, tied with Bombay Sapphire at **4.37 million nine-liter cases** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEZOxK4rXtYJHouvNfNNB8YC4uN48HwBOV69xZ9xn9Ep8M5vAV1EpPvmcu2VF2_n_BBAhXnrkn3TlIirylgVLXhZ3PLFU1DiwAGAWTqjR4KSlStqMjAo41CPhLDm5PKgcq-nQwf6P8u0ABKtfAr_bEP38RcWpOYxbl9MgX0xh0KafH9, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGHQZLETUuQNd1MmP8dTLVMsUpEf8TEIPbVZLiQoJ2m8-tKiAEHAHYHnhpHiqvF7mqDKy5-yz58QlrUqq_LaxaRdMnD-B75ob4bR9RG1ZNPjmfkSlVQZmirlVXOrFpESImu0pATXDs3S0Vy9ITr9g0okTkALCrJcjjUtjhmBObl-YezVGGLOVEyIz9rcAg6bmGpAIM=].\n*   In **2023**, it was the **second-biggest selling gin brand globally by volume** among leading international brands, with **4.7 million nine-liter cases**, despite a **15.7% decline in volume sales** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQETVqarv5K9D9rN_5zuk0_Q39i76A_wvkAQ7R9WiU51g6NRx9sqPGfaYJB-uXqM5jVhty4vfLuGSKDAqqtSV197Xn1aS9Sh8K1U-DxhNK5687ZdaKHYrKFOa7dIsTrGLeOxQEsUgrSekM2PeHJEDOgGwKYYVZFipvGM1RjP, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGHQZLETUuQNd1MmP8dTLVMsUpEf8TEIPbVZLiQoJ2m8-tKiAEHAHYHnhpHiqvF7mqDKy5-yz58QlrUqq_LaxaRdMnD-B75ob4bR9RG1ZNPjmfkSlVQZmirlVXOrFpESImu0pATXDs3S0Vy9ITr9g0okTkALCrJcjjUtjhmBObl-YezVGGLOVEyIz9rcAg6bmGpAIM=, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2024/06/the-top-10-best-selling-gin-brands/, https://www.just-drinks.com/news/the-worlds-top-10-best-selling-gin-brands-data/]. This positioned it behind Gordon's and 90,000 cases ahead of Bombay Sapphire [https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2024/06/the-top-10-best-selling-gin-brands/, https://www.just-drinks.com/news/the-top-10-best-selling-gin-brands-data/].\n*   In the US, Tanqueray was the **second-largest gin brand by sales volume in 2021**, with **1.36 million nine-liter cases** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEZOxK4rXtYJHouvNfNNB8YC4uN48HwBOV69xZ9xn9Ep8M5vAV1EpPvmcu2VF2_n_BBAhXnrkn3TlIirylgVLXhZ3PLFU1DiwAGAWTqjR4KSlStqMjAo41CPhLDm5PKgcq-nQwf6P8u0ABKtfAr_bEP38RcWpOYxbl9MgX0xh0KafH9, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFKZDhGXzmkY89xrh311_0uY_scQDSUM5_eMA3usBBWPcqHjz8dYebVcK2codutPkXtIOxddZajlFkxQhf-A-Yr7TsrRoBZ4YOYycEdjWZi6ipzFspkJ_42IXWjwnDY2HMftjVSq785-RZFpU=]. Seagram's Gin was the top-selling brand in 2021 with 1.81 million cases [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGVX9st3SyICdkHgFcWscU_9ZK8DfiCzP9KZSSlu1--njAJqkw19BzhuxvpX2D7IvMOv0PDHFu6r2CiYsti_Mc_P9lxffIGhJJVaxX9ULK9J1Uz6iqeNHToxDLfrg6LQ3EBMeCjNt5Fsne0dO1ltRQfl_FnBtCpn77cN7mH1wih].\n*   **[single-source]** Tanqueray was the **largest gin brand in the U.S. at 1.35 million cases in 2024** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE2aGOZzt1wzSKIBxKANbasUob1NXIDsM_NDB4CV0Db5OgLuVKLI1j_TsXJwIZTOJJXugpeJlQiPfpT89s_dLAB0T_6nl7dqebY51XDDcNXRnSdiJj2ufwrEWVgXrOeCii_utkmPos-n_xXbVBwwNbB16zv0xudmq-3Sowb]. This claim, while indicating strong performance, should be viewed in context with other leading brands and the distinction between premium and overall volume. It aligns with its strong on-trade presence, being the top choice for **24% of bars** polled in 2025 [https://www.drinksint.com/news/fullstory.php/aid/10419/Tanqueray_No._Ten_unveils_new_bottle_design.html, https://www.barbizmag.com/news/top-selling-gin-brands-2025/]. In 2025, Tanqueray was chosen by **24% of polled bars** [https://www.drinksint.com/news/fullstory.php/aid/11099/The_World_s_50_Best_Bars_Brands_Report_2025.html, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2025/01/the-worlds-50-best-bars-brands-report-2025/]. In 2026, Tanqueray was named the bestselling gin in **30% of polled bars** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEVMv1KBSRj5Mx0QA0ASov--aPkD8xdslB9D_ElEy2awkFOcRI2KxFrMHf_uW5jKFXFOdmxOuc_stCrRezaRZM7LcOU4l9XL1k_MbZOvbXdx2sBM3bA4Uw_huUFnyof6lSigVcp_3rh4ZtBJSGfuCx9U5KTkJUSSHOkUWEDLs9-9hsHkEa4w1r4P-Q=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG1H-8BVGwPxNHt4ZMfdJPgPgtum2smQTNwZFebFFUCleV_L9I3fiT0qwa_2D80ixMPipE1YU_AG4Sz6BrmSiCj6tk9YK6yY0Y7B6bSde56fohg52MBUfzt9rqKe-j6bJ1vMRIj8H732Wl9EPYCejzbxJPOm1xercU=].\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"4. Target Market","content":"\nTanqueray primarily targets spirit drinkers aged **28-38** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGn5ja8WhJrugj5Fcq4ufjMSzR2J6-49PSMbE2UvI_TU24MNjzLY414J-Bm8BJDtn4ZRCN4WFkYWQB3I14qu6VP7oizFEkebpl9NoFuBw6D9XYOtv_voezGa__NVo-lCLCbdl0yQHZS7e7-BF_z-rWa_WzM7XVJfrGck6RCFt4ONpoCNjX5ocNMlhE8e2buz9pX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZfXKb6p5zffxijJFUiBCXk6NJG1CYxenFSEoDejFvqmLtQ8O1xndYOAi4mQBxiAxfs3ML5Elt1vqUjGPTX13hNBzR94ZCNNjsexnq5MSYjD6go1tRYbkLujX7Tuvyqia9vxSnz8vHn8vxRG26H-NGww==]. Diageo's broader customer base for brands like Tanqueray includes **25-45 urban professionals with mid-to-high disposable incomes, valuing quality and prestige** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZfXKb6p5zffxijJFUiBCXk6NJG1CYxenFSEoDejFvqmLtQ8O1xndYOAi4mQBxiAxfs3ML5Elt1vqUjGPTX13hNBzR94ZCNNjsexnq5MSYjD6go1tRYbkLujX7Tuvyqia9vxSnz8vHn8vxRG26H-NGww==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGn5ja8WhJrugj5Fcq4ufjMSzR2J6-49PSMbE2UvI_TU24MNjzLY414J-Bm8BJDtn4ZRCN4WFkYWQB3I14qu6VP7oizFEkebpl9NoFuBw6D9XYOtv_voezGa__NVo-lCLCbdl0yQHZS7e7-BF_z-rWa_WzM7XVJfrGck6RCFt4ONpoCNjX5ocNMlhE8e2buz9pX]. Younger demographics, particularly Millennials and Gen Z, are increasingly pivotal in driving growth for both gin and RTDs. For instance, **42% of US gin drinkers are aged 21-34**, and **84% of RTD drinkers are under 55** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGiDo5_YaD18n_J7PefgWZyy23lYHJPiB7tvs16ARN6QzjvIr1SDe9rKnRRRdzbabZ9HaAfrpmCNPqaJXH5jCXaqyEpRIm3D59g4XpQwABMHnXP4rkeQMVheXZjYLAGT9BlXys1KBiufN46HbOqVtJXQwt6CVrz35555KG5rcivsCQ0zKfJ1RJREVluKFHrtGk=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEmewQikPmpH9UCqulAv_ev2Y1VR4E0o7KSHVx9kYB-eXAVDDU8r0fpxUwX3XjbNWaBn3ao_UQHvzVw974VvUmslPWG7DuQjJFvkrKTH9uIcj9xEdB35KGgNJdJ_yWvI9WmK_h_GvNR_Y-AakmpgIx5E75yVB2JVbO-X36hjtVThPjks--YUD5iK-bMV8m6G7pwnQxzdlQEnNBR47Z0].\n\nPsychographically, Tanqueray appeals to consumers who value **bold, premium, and classic experiences** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGn5ja8WhJrugj5Fcq4ufjMSzR2J6-49PSMbE2UvI_TU24MNjzLY414J-Bm8BJDtn4ZRCN4WFkYWQB3I14qu6VP7oizFEkebpl9NoFuBw6D9XYOtv_voezGa__NVo-lCLCbdl0yQHZS7e7-BF_z-rWa_WzM7XVJfrGck6RCFt4ONpoCNjX5ocNMlhE8e2buz9pX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEYcyL4jVPWfOg4LTWZLosCo8Jwexgv9cfuheV3o-TcPsMyihDiFItcUaDWkqFZevtecZVi3ZHwp_lC3VnCw4szq_R4bb-GF0x7JF_4M5ieq2sIHkayXxJJ]. Its brand extensions (e.g., Rangpur, No. Ten) target consumers seeking **new, unique, and high-quality offerings** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGn5ja8WhJrugj5Fcq4ufjMSzR2J6-49PSMbE2UvI_TU24MNjzLY414J-Bm8BJDtn4ZRCN4WFkYWQB3I14qu6VP7oizFEkebpl9NoFuBw6D9XYOtv_voezGa__NVo-lCLCbdl0yQHZS7e7-BF_z-rWa_WzM7XVJfrGck6RCFt4ONpoCNjX5ocNMlhE8e2buz9pX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFY8OPq_FZHgMVqD75qGw_45-mBWespliVnDu8NNf_MZMuU59Kev0qkJT6S52vSE-UJu5t1DgQBQYi9TI4s5wbWgKxD8yHE-lRMoF6HbnXSkFKAmdFAtBjheaURocBzYleuG3_ubO572u_gC8BpbiEKqQ84Rp8AMMFAcIqAMWX7QCM2d9mdt1Y6TluywoV9iXzbbe-fQvB3YGIy675jXPs=].\n\nTanqueray is a global brand enjoyed in **over 180 countries worldwide** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGn5ja8WhJrugj5Fcq4ufjMSzR2J6-49PSMbE2UvI_TU24MNjzLY414J-Bm8BJDtn4ZRCN4WFkYWQB3I14qu6VP7oizFEkebpl9NoFuBw6D9XYOtv_voezGa__NVo-lCLCbdl0yQHZS7e7-BF_z-rWa_WzM7XVJfrGck6RCFt4ONpoCNjX5ocNMlhE8e2buz9pX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEV2h-PketG483gvoBIjQqniTF1i1oYX1RmWshx842lvTGGbYgIUcAZfobkkogik0X3HT-nC6Qe0k4X1d3y0Q8xozXeQTAy9elEokqL6ZPoRvt2FvG2RCSgl7irBtLVTxY=], with the **United States as its largest market** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGn5ja8WhJrugj5Fcq4ufjMSzR2J6-49PSMbE2UvI_TU24MNjzLY414J-Bm8BJDtn4ZRCN4WFkYWQB3I14qu6VP7oizFEkebpl9NoFuBw6D9XYOtv_voezGa__NVo-lCLCbdl0yQHZS7e7-BF_z-rWa_WzM7XVJfrGck6RCFt4ONpoCNjX5ocNMlhE8e2buz9pX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZfXKb6p5zffxijJFUiBCXk6NJG1CYxenFSEoDejFvqmLtQ8O1xndYOAi4mQBxiAxfs3ML5Elt1vqUjGPTX13hNBzR94ZCNNjsexnq5MSYjD6go1tRYbkLujX7Tuvyqia9vxSnz8vHn8vxRG26H-NGww==]. It showed significant organic net sales growth in **Europe (+41%)** and **Latin America and the Caribbean (+40%)** in H2 2021 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGn5ja8WhJrugj5Fcq4ufjMSzR2J6-49PSMbE2UvI_TU24MNjzLY414J-Bm8BJDtn4ZRCN4WFkYWQB3I14qu6VP7oizFEkebpl9NoFuBw6D9XYOtv_voezGa__NVo-lCLCbdl0yQHZS7e7-BF_z-rWa_WzM7XVJfrGck6RCFt4ONpoCNjX5ocNMlhE8e2buz9pX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEd-cONQed6pIYOqdipyfN2AGQJU-C-uG5Rum90VbHIToj4aheaM_zI034nGiHaLv8pO9a0nY2xeYgsoXwpMUcxaUacAjTtUPh8ighBAJLQ0_vSHhzCAEYvsBUutzIkCwNhm6AAQQbjE_3eaGoA-hmSBmiVLp0IlS57bMghLF-7wUO5st017ecn8CM=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFDDeWBU6exAPibBm946m2VdJJo4HKbQbN8Q1R7ywKv2L_1021cXvHXQAk6pGekEohj0gGSaB470yJf3yRMC10veosAWX0XUMNLiYyuo2ECyqdZISxSMQ7ptn-3b_QZfH3SzdyOCPjFns5ixdAPiYraNz-7c4Q5sm4QkP5of, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGkiDuHXV1E1Kdex3j198t7RCduss6sCAcZBjCmx2lGixaoeOslbDLEY5x2s6J6bgK_GOFltmiEMvA7rhHQF4GSen9Exdk_fDyfYU1lzAZcro-sDGkS3Z2f3EDLbmQtHwlUhEOOVPQyLrZETcyU243cCtJZe767reV3Ghmtb7yugAoKKICQCvAhy1VSwsNhK6TIgGEhQ6FWmXEMheblv7sZviLrMV6Yzi0qaK_Mbg==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQENSZW14KSkt0oxIkN4Z-PtxqXAYzcN9HKSMQa8i1oM46LiF4WieTFUJGtk6ftpDjZw_WeMG1kdrwSRdvZbZi8J9cmRfEF9N4KCrj8-hyKMBS5169Yqed4UI6IbkRqLQvcje7gq8BHMku4R0J1V2vSWcjSGSNuCSNcbblEqZiwTkFfa8qo4DQJ]. **[single-source]** Diageo's overall sales in Latin America & Caribbean rose by 9.2% in fiscal 2025 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZfXKb6p5zffxijJFUiBCXk6NJG1CYxenFSEoDejFvqmLtQ8O1xndYOAi4mQBxiAxfs3ML5Elt1vqUjGPTX13hNBzR94ZCNNjsexnq5MSYjD6go1tRYbkLujX7Tuvyqia9vxSnz8vHn8vxRG26H-NGww==]. Europe held a **USD 6.8 billion revenue share and a 42.57% market share** in the global gin market in 2025 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHCYZi8YXxqRDURsWqtMJpMayifbciJOpyCC45kAzP2wDJAnpC3vJk1s858JnQ3Bvw2vR9byNR5pvlIDAi9L4g-Ixtyb-rZmTnU86zSUl2PWsf-u34KO0IFwBCIgknDgjfq4MuEX4y9VQxKvWO8, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHO9fPQr-oxo0FyE-Szhy3fs2IYLRmSAPcNs4igqMQQ2inNWoxsURJ1Reyuq-RHiBzJB0EuaOCzP6gsQrkZoZmN61TqDdd16kt3PYaZNSy6tKL_Nw9eiJeMwK_R2gDTecKwHPrYUs4pG6oIN-YQx_c=].\n\nKey drinking occasions for Tanqueray include **classic gin and tonics, martinis, and a wide array of cocktails** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGn5ja8WhJrugj5Fcq4ufjMSzR2J6-49PSMbE2UvI_TU24MNjzLY414J-Bm8BJDtn4ZRCN4WFkYWQB3I14qu6VP7oizFEkebpl9NoFuBw6D9XYOtv_voezGa__NVo-lCLCbdl0yQHZS7e7-BF_z-rWa_WzM7XVJfrGck6RCFt4ONpoCNjX5ocNMlhE8e2buz9pX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFY8OPq_FZHgMVqD75qGw_45-mBWespliVnDu8NNf_MZMuU59Kev0qkJT6S52vSE-UJu5t1DgQBQYi9TI4s5wbWgKxD8yHE-lRMoF6HbnXSkFKAmdFAtBjheaURocBzYleuG3_ubO572u_gC8BpbiEKqQ84Rp8AMMFAcIqAMWX7QCM2d9mdt1Y6TluywoV9iXzbbe-fQvB3YGIy675jXPs=]. It is often positioned to **'start the night right'** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGn5ja8WhJrugj5Fcq4ufjMSzR2J6-49PSMbE2UvI_TU24MNjzLY414J-Bm8BJDtn4ZRCN4WFkYWQB3I14qu6VP7oizFEkebpl9NoFuBw6D9XYOtv_voezGa__NVo-lCLCbdl0yQHZS7e7-BF_z-rWa_WzM7XVJfrGck6RCFt4ONpoCNjX5ocNMlhE8e2buz9pX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFIlfKnOCWgsupVRk8JublgrMhFLWv_6_gTw2wqwD14fYUu26I_lDmLKJHktMb-TRStFbjRMKEmc2BmuR07mjgQedglHA7URTuEKBOT7hrbz-eOKmzRF1fGwnH7ALuFBT-VPIsfBo5z4PS1OSv10t2gY7KqRZZjXivV]. Tanqueray No. Ten is specifically targeted at the **martini market and is ideal for fruit cocktails** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGn5ja8WhJrugj5Fcq4ufjMSzR2J6-49PSMbE2UvI_TU24MNjzLY414J-Bm8BJDtn4ZRCN4WFkYWQB3I14qu6VP7oizFEkebpl9NoFuBw6D9XYOtv_voezGa__NVo-lCLCbdl0yQHZS7e7-BF_z-rWa_WzM7XVJfrGck6RCFt4ONpoCNjX5ocNMlhE8e2buz9pX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFY8OPq_FZHgMVqD75qGw_45-mBWespliVnDu8NNf_MZMuU59Kev0qkJT6S52vSE-UJu5t1DgQBQYi9TI4s5wbWgKxD8yHE-lRMoF6HbnXSkFKAmdFAtBjheaURocBzYleuG3_ubO572u_gC8BpbiEKqQ84Rp8AMMFAcIqAMWX7QCM2d9mdt1Y6TluywoV9iXzbbe-fQvB3YGIy675jXPs=]. Flavored variants, like Tanqueray Sevilla Orange, are popular for **vibrant, citrusy drinks perfect for brunch or refreshing afternoons** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGn5ja8WhJrugj5Fcq4ufjMSzR2J6-49PSMbE2UvI_TU24MNjzLY414J-Bm8BJDtn4ZRCN4WFkYWQB3I14qu6VP7oizFEkebpl9NoFuBw6D9XYOtv_voezGa__NVo-lCLCbdl0yQHZS7e7-BF_z-rWa_WzM7XVJfrGck6RCFt4ONpoCNjX5ocNMlhE8e2buz9pX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFY8OPq_FZHgMVqD75qGw_45-mBWespliVnDu8NNf_MZMuU59Kev0qkJT6S52vSE-UJu5t1DgQBQYi9TI4s5wbWgKxD8yHE-lRMoF6HbnXSkFKAmdFAtBjheaURocBzYleuG3_ubO572u_gC8BpbiEKqQ84Rp8AMMFAcIqAMWX7QCM2d9mdt1Y6TluywoV9iXzbbe-fQvB3YGIy675jXPs=]. The brand has also introduced **Tanqueray 0.0%** to cater to the growing moderation movement and health-conscious consumers [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGn5ja8WhJrugj5Fcq4ufjMSzR2J6-49PSMbE2UvI_TU24MNjzLY414J-Bm8BJDtn4ZRCN4WFkYWQB3I14qu6VP7oizFEkebpl9NoFuBw6D9XYOtv_voezGa__NVo-lCLCbdl0yQHZS7e7-BF_z-rWa_WzM7XVJfrGck6RCFt4ONpoCNjX5ocNMlhE8e2buz9pX, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGZfXKb6p5zffxijJFUiBCXk6NJG1CYxenFSEoDejFvqmLtQ8O1xndYOAi4mQBxiAxfs3ML5Elt1vqUjGPTX13hNBzR94ZCNNjsexnq5MSYjD6go1tRYbkLujX7Tuvyqia9vxSnz8vHn8vxRG26H-NGww==].\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"5. Campaigns","content":"\n*   **2021: 'House of Gucci' Digital Campaign:** Tanqueray partnered with the Ridley Scott Agency for a digital campaign tied to the 'House of Gucci' film, featuring the Tanqueray Martini with a Twist [https://www.mediapost.com/publications/article/368297/tanqueray-stars-in-house-of-gucci-film-digital.html, https://wehotimes.com/tanquerays-martini-with-a-twist-premiers-in-new-house-of-gucci-film/, https://www.justluxe.com/lifestyle/dining/feature-1977797.php].\n*   **February 2022: Anomaly London Appointment [single-source]:** Diageo appointed Anomaly London as global brand strategy and creative partner for Tanqueray [https://www.thedrum.com/news/2023/02/16/tanqueray-gin-unveils-first-global-campaign-5-years-after-moving-account-anomaly].\n*   **2023: 'Let's Live Magnificently' Global Campaign:** Tanqueray launched its first global campaign in four years, 'Let's Live Magnificently', created by Anomaly London, encouraging consumers to elevate everyday moments [https://www.fabnews.live/lets-live-magnificently-tanqueray-shakes-things-up-with-new-global-brand-campaign/, https://www.thedrum.com/news/2023/02/16/tanqueray-gin-unveils-first-global-campaign-5-years-after-moving-account-anomaly, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2023/02/tanqueray-unveils-global-campaign/].\n*   **June 2024: 'Fancy Hour' Campaign:** Tanqueray launched the 'Fancy Hour' campaign, inviting cocktail enthusiasts to elevate occasions with a martini, partnering with OpenTable [https://www.multivu.com/players/English/9270051-tanqueray-fancy-hour-martini-month/, https://sensational-sips.com/walking-the-talk-with-tanqueray/].\n*   **Late 2024/Early 2025: 'Classic or Nothing' Campaign:** Tanqueray London Gin launched the 'Classic or Nothing' campaign, emphasizing its heritage and iconic status, with experiential activations like the 'Classic or Nothing Diner' [https://www.trendhunter.com/trends/classic-or-nothing, https://www.mediapost.com/publications/article/396030/tanqueray-london-gin-launches-classic-or-nothing.html, https://www.bevnet.com/news/2024/tanqueray-introduces-a-bold-invitation-to-enjoy-classic-cocktails-with-the-brands-new-classic-or-nothing-campaign]. This campaign was a digital-first social media initiative in the US [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEmgZlBYiPPufLaibycmBBsgDcIATbdf_1oAfpk8G_dEaqDonErTLWk4T3z9y0t79OX9vICRZ388tPM-i3Vbiuvg3NagBBtuVth1KeZ8jxl7qMgXSjHXekVSWlUsqgVpXdnTSu-eycKj73aVEm134HPJAs0H0xOyuWWeZbL0_1l7JDGA30, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGpNlFedCiBUSX7rq2-6h_9ZbzW5w3MY0rwyMtwXXU9DYj3f75sLGfZTyZIgLFgghUYrk4GQ9jhEMgWG1s-xEOhUK51j_db5lsJxCR601hFM7xJ4dZUM6SdXGfWibz0R9KJw_46fkLRxBBh].\n*   **January/February 2026: 'There's an N and an O in every ICON' with Sarah Jessica Parker:** Tanqueray launched a global partnership with Sarah Jessica Parker centered on the theme 'There's an N and an O in every ICON' and the concept of '300 No's' [https://www.designrush.com/news/tanqueray-sarah-jessica-parker-campaign, https://www.theginguild.com/tanqueray-announces-global-campaign-with-sarah-jessica-parker/, https://www.adsoftheworld.com/campaigns/300-nos]. This partnership is a significant global investment by Diageo aimed at strengthening Tanqueray's premium positioning and connecting with contemporary lifestyle through on and offline brand experiences and digital content across Instagram, TikTok, and YouTube [https://www.diageo.com/news-media/news-releases/2026/sarah-jessica-parker-joins-tanqueray-as-global-ambassador, https://www.marketingweek.com/tanqueray-sarah-jessica-parker-partnership/]. The '300 No's' concept is rooted in founder Charles Tanqueray's meticulous pursuit of perfection, reportedly rejecting 300 recipes before settling on the iconic London Dry Gin formula [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGMYCp3y7wrj16jVwJvetBqvSxSvhgwiCuAenkS0KfWq5_nMygUPL7NLb7UOx8BmkTRXEVSoTuil0MxAOrnTxDASVk2qX70uUNMolTB92fdzkvVHQaE4BXdJdxSuELD6Rp3MW8tjAwzinq4C3na7dg7YFa2_ScF2w0kI8NfRGyvb88c4W6Y2e1q2BlxWbRekAEuQ==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFsXKeogblohNVw8F2bQXM7CBHbhEabkLoJxlVYD19-qbk-VMeYjzfzMn-Fa9wSdjfdhv6VUp1MsVLn0aMdudDqi_xfca9eope1CZVtE53UcetfuJp3Yeku18_9w-Bd-uwTNciLt2UcmKdQKyyK2G7A6ouBZYjW8r5cJplvL2SmsNPvv1z_jTStQfeKb03ScHyr0AIPFglZCI=]. **[single-source]** Sarah Jessica Parker was announced as Tanqueray's first global ambassador for this campaign [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE2aGOZzt1wzSKIBxKANbasUob1NXIDsM_NDB4CV0Db5OgLuVKLI1j_TsXJwIZTOJJXugpeJlQiPfpT89s_dLAB0T_6nl7dqebY51XDDcNXRnSdiJj2ufwrEWVgXrOeCii_utkmPos-n_xXbVBwwNbB16zv0xudmq-3Sowb].\n*   **2026: Tanqueray Flor de Sevilla 0.0% Launch:** Expanding its no- and low-alcohol (NoLo) portfolio, Tanqueray introduced an alcohol-free version of its popular Flor de Sevilla gin, aiming to capture a larger share of the growing moderation trend [https://www.diageo.com/news-media/news-releases/2026/tanqueray-00-expands-with-flor-de-sevilla-variant].\n*   **2026: Tanqueray Royale Sampling Campaign (UK):** A sampling campaign for Tanqueray Royale in the UK demonstrated strong consumer engagement, with **25% of consumers purchasing the product and 81% recommending it** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHB-l3wChbrS5R0f-oxhNKJGiQHlhPT7wQ3K79I_RbswJI-ZeqDujDbxJPAEmX040RQxZhiy8TrP_n-pGHXfhgNI7W7ZnjPX4IK_yBCCKL0w2Lm9UoBuys_QXZBgQy-pdVIOJOVnw==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGv21ZBpV2Waca6b14TRJ1qYQy_trzEVrjJzBCpjhYhySQiDsy0Nykrb9yLyDwp85D49nfWzR69r30PW_GakwlrzNaOGJqGNfyyXbMVASjz2jZJw31dHSLRSzR6EgVfYCxhnSaBTZ48eafHdVV5V7Pa7fh1j7acATFN5xBRxlN_pizGfb9jbTP58eh_Rw==].\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"6. Current Strategy","content":"\nTanqueray's current strategy appears to be a multi-pronged approach to address declining core volumes while capitalizing on premiumization and emerging trends:\n\n*   **Premiumization Focus:** Tanqueray No. TEN, its super-premium extension, has shown consistent growth [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE2aGOZzt1wzSKIBxKANbasUob1NXIDsM_NDB4CV0Db5OgLuVKLI1j_TsXJwIZTOJJXugpeJlQiPfpT89s_dLAB0T_6nl7dqebY51XDDcNXRnSdiJj2ufwrEWVgXrOeCii_utkmPos-n_xXbVBwwNbB16zv0xudmq-3Sowb]. A new bottle design for Tanqueray No. TEN debuted in April 2024 [single-source: https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE2aGOZzt1wzSKIBxKANbasUob1NXIDsM_NDB4CV0Db5OgLuVKLI1j_TsXJwIZTOJJXugpeJlQiPfpT89s_dLAB0T_6nl7dqebY51XDDcNXRnSdiJj2ufwrEWVgXrOeCii_utkmPos-n_xXbVBwwNbB16zv0xudmq-3Sowb]. The premium gin segment is a key growth driver, expanding at a CAGR of **7.9% from 2025 to 2034**, significantly outpacing the overall market's 6.2% CAGR [https://www.iwsrcan.com/insights/premium-gin-market-growth-forecast/, https://www.grandviewresearch.com/industry-analysis/premium-gin-market]. The premium and super-premium gin segments collectively grew at approximately **9.3% annually between 2021 and 2025** [https://www.iwsrcan.com/news/premium-spirits-growth-continues-to-outpace-total-spirits-in-2022/]. By 2025, approximately **27% of U.S. gin sales by value** were in the super-premium category [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGof41zxyOZTdyOnsPuDOfX9yywQPgPJqSYC1PFGK8UVyxjdsroR77ydJXEovQ7W9N-01X4CaST-Kzx-UdpLVUdGjnsrK3i5fFiJmfwwdkOgWd3IpeIQcxT8c8qhiftvqPFIvMFRArg-Tc2seeAEMZ_ZkSPcYc8Sq2HgU, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQExJIpDjhj-nHHfpPkUv_Hg3MnDhbcrAwZySg47fbcNAi0l8K6aA9lFU4VwX94bJWevwOAxsgiwg1JXXeENHfnhl5wB69aYV58hGEnO_X5HJCnKTt713bX79qM4GlP0kcezhUTuA52AGPWcM9aiVMZz7bRG13YISVqgbgYXwRyof4R5r88LJa-Rt6lxaMkkIl4AVZ4]. The super-premium gin category in the U.S. saw a **187% increase in volume sales from 2019 to 2024**, though it represented only **8% of total cases sold in 2024** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGNxu4UhSCVMIXYOfcdyc5h78fplunrPDld8NEVO9K3KuPaQzqXZzKQSdecaLC6hRtN5_FAtvTM3d4m8dJtdCZuKlRZ7u77cCYLdlKd-YVVYt1Gc4diPm0y2nMHpgdk_cMt15bwwEJN2gZhZKiWO5XBwYNtQIxxiJC_O5qWQqi2thIpTLdLrzmF6C6qyBY8IQ, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGgflEj0JseF-qWSnf4RbikJTfSGcZipmPsQ3q8WULlLk_2EHg4VfwFGHOPMig76eNhroKiiD3K3zZuofH10vzRGblY2reJsJyX404fQeH_eSuFLgNvB5BJvbMtIoGv0Vlujvo2iQOApleeTlItxa2CvHwzm1StYRZtY1gkQ4UoYRKIIayQ].\n*   **Product Diversification & Innovation:** In 2021, Tanqueray launched an **alcohol-free variant, a blackcurrant flavor, and ready-to-drink (RTD) gin and tonics** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE2aGOZzt1wzSKIBxKANbasUob1NXIDsM_NDB4CV0Db5OgLuVKLI1j_TsXJwIZTOJJXugpeJlQiPfpT89s_dLAB0T_6nl7dqebY51XDDcNXRnSdiJj2ufwrEWVgXrOeCii_utkmPos-n_xXbVBwwNbB16zv0xudmq-3Sowb, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFnDc1rdxwnQ49hVl6exYWp-o8k8QpQGD3mo-L47HWUFNltxNRQUdBElHa3s_zqG2u3Cqu-hai_fxJKyfnWY_pkDSW4q4iFynT3NWBHVdxCc-B8Y_2nwsFeVP0Pc6XA3mPYYVCqeA2nwi46aribn6waEozUuPve75sOLgsgRlbuDLjgGtO1Xvd119vlFAjCA_vTeUyoWBZ9DpjHT9I3pVe]. Tanqueray launched its bottled RTD gin and tonics in **2019** and introduced new RTD cans in **April 2021** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH7XJSTtR3aMHb3pzFurE_-8tYNRjuoSgGL9l-Rdxpj74QbbJ15_94B9rQmMFuZsPFAnQEHpMUNPtpcmL3VwnEJT8wEbEAIDxLHzqznU0ywHFDCZ0R-K24TZPz0K8v6jOZxKqMalrmObbN2iLFlyJeBHI2u26aTMzc7zc63iZsTeuOYXLv9hYsn3QPsRkQgXs0, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG6RayS1-kckb2A3Qcr2whIzgz_j27oPZpQw1tLQIOt9GmQQpUs9U4gR1IPlE6dHQFE-3BnqpyT_trWWiupSOYRQ8f9JVRiyxeuUJbk2lXJBP5UFrqDiRIkgMETBYyyFKE6Iw1UvuCrHtQGQfPktNbSU8U6iVic3stUsrsDr3MnikbqqGMHTbgxsuXa]. Tanqueray 0.0% alcohol-free spirit was launched in **March 2021** in the UK and Spain [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGO_NiJpvMBSh1jqWizDyNDQP894Ve6nBeasPMk-y0zcj_iBOp1wpu23BVUELKXAhkpURFXHZ-G4wpNbHNv8BdfVDEOWkvHe4PStSYfKl5D3xg0lKRth14ZabuM7fV7hk4Lddsl0jhMdmS6se2sGyeONbeI470hcvkh7PbA6XJ0V15U-76CPu6yBoekVQkksG_FslbaYALbwjvlMBWB1WEECz95uw153hM35vIP, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGo-3YwyEXBhqgYrbcP1kbONfySfxdl4EK6tJ47v4h9ymYJixcL68cJTWdy7MvFgrNbWngBby1VjQWb1_LNUvXvzWlbR4K]. Tanqueray Flor de Sevilla, a blood-orange variant, saw global expansion by 2024 and increased female trial rates by 35% in the United Kingdom's off-trade channels [single-source: https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHBWc4zd7sSersQF8OSwvqOE2d_VGZknClHg06HhSZlaJOszMyQYAs3U8e_3FFJapeeq0cf8_k39QG-1CwoexuFb7ugFCz9OJxkhSx2pVDsqve27Wk7h4IWda3LuxddvBTL-QsD8INQL41u8jfDCzX-WzvoSh8fA-K7g7lHZ-RzCWX47RJACzXfwzX6ZpLth93gwzTTXuc32gzt7b-m9AGBSYAepAOYcVt5iS-3zSLFyOZtfsHsUS-5ZVeZINNeNiinxFc4w6FEofHsnk0P4gmvYnNtMg03ubs1SpUCFEy698-0-lAkq9t_kbVX]. In November 2025, Diageo launched a new line of organic gins [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGof41zxyOZTdyOnsPuDOfX9yywQPgPJqSYC1PFGK8UVyxjdsroR77ydJXEovQ7W9N-01X4CaST-Kzx-UdpLVUdGjnsrK3i5fFiJmfwwdkOgWd3IpeIQcxT8c8qhiftvqPFIvMFRArg-Tc2seeAEMZ_ZkSPcYc8Sq2HgU, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH2el6eV0vmRbqaljo7zeCHBm4jRjYtiAiCxeU1xmbI9m7zHf_WL7L0MQNeTE6wj67MdVH9h_JkdoxtetR1mjNYMlva7f70WlncTB_5LvXVJCfnKDfEDnqRh0KdzWcp_jjQcmHwyRKAU6Dd27pFqIPlVxHaqoj-DMcNsdx9q5nVzUSK-XZbol72CopcAnQrjX0yc2K6k-Bz2g50NJy5]. Diageo has strategically re-focused on the RTD segment, viewing it as a crucial tool for recruiting new drinkers and driving growth, particularly in the context of slowing standalone spirits sales in some mature markets [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGaf-wTyl0Ht1NxfGyK8yXSx9l5k5Uf-O0ZiZfAhwl58F_oOlvvzAWOzAL7WmKYf1E8Z3CC78jjH0rBUZOd_WJKtNMiOhLwHPK2dE8lDqdWRbkCZmbripP_PN4mcGGOTEFz6TDnOnuhFtcOE2GayIsx-9lDEFNIljt_K6JEAXP1XmVa5K_xSQ6M309BmhwBY_aX4R19xlIXygygjjZIK4ZpZSldJ_sy4A==]. The launch of Tanqueray Flor de Sevilla 0.0% in 2026 further addresses the growing consumer demand for NoLo options, with **38% of consumers actively looking to moderate alcohol intake** [https://www.diageo.com/news-media/news-releases/2026/tanqueray-00-expands-with-flor-de-sevilla-variant, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGaf-wTyl0Ht1NxfGyK8yXSx9l5k5Uf-O0ZiZfAhwl58F_oOlvvzAWOzAL7WmKYf1E8Z3CC78jjH0rBUZOd_WJKtNMiOhLwHPK2dE8lDqdWRbkCZmbripP_PN4mcGGOTEFz6TDnOnuhFtcOE2GayIsx-9lDEFNIljt_K6JEAXP1XmVa5K_xSQ6M309BmhwBY_aX4R19xlIXygygjjZIK4ZpZSldJ_sy4A==].\n*   **Marketing & Brand Reinforcement:** Diageo increased its global marketing investment by **5.6% in the year to June 30, 2023** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFBCgRbcg7AUerm-e80dMJLUx63u1AzjyRypl6vGWqq0UomEsNSYPYnJOs3p2oCVlyaGm8jqjCBF07RrRT2b0WswRhkVmT-I4RLIU_Y0DEyE2WJsHenJ0Vzhj7wwjpjH9RQr4c8kW5WXuX0VO9RAT41ADL52hi1ibMfKAJtf_TIIgdmqBwzznhRL0=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHLLpBoTXrMCT9slVM8Pvdq82f0rzn8661QA0LndM0xaqbhekzwgCb5JOEWpcDFs7u1_8u3mAJoBQf-Qol72A4ZoyhFpq0WcdfyydgOx4zjs3sMFNwInv3KgoNjcf_1Fu8Jz_dCUowUluK6w2oRe-FOG1gVuH8SNln08yUFUhNz-aiWDuSURzKb0iSLS5ekWWKPw=], and by **6% year-over-year for Fiscal Year 2024 (FY24)** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQESRqKwG5J9LugES2VtOk_EE_xB6fAzgZj7RPoS19qOVSp2aMB7T1J7bCnAgK0-7_Gv2CyFmKTYsWTBF5H7N3XjMeo7uBlDeXdpNWClzbTfSKYGj-c4E6VyIoQI43DT-2MzJaz5wSynYGBRnpBzMLTZpkYauV0bO3omJXNq], prioritizing brands including Tanqueray. The 'Classic or Nothing' campaign (late 2024/early 2025) emphasizes heritage, quality, and classic cocktails [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE2aGOZzt1wzSKIBxKANbasUob1NXIDsM_NDB4CV0Db5OgLuVKLI1j_TsXJwIZTOJJXugpeJlQiPfpT89s_dLAB0T_6nl7dqebY51XDDcNXRnSdiJj2ufwrEWVgXrOeCii_utkmPos-n_xK3pVBwwNbB16zv0xudmq-3Sowb, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGnNMAofrEBBrxGt210cbEkjCdERuyglEnBQ7KUL4bkAJHGzNHkt4N1WwRSsCNWWakULvK2qbw6DzsMxVsGUdTYdU2d7dqHYWg9Vg7c2hp4C2l0GimbXl8sacsQPPuG9RtlMH0BHgYpHm5fbRo7uUuLvL8NeD3XyT6KsFEy8_mZQzOS1VfxYaHZbEg1Gl9sjcMVIxMO3Mg9yrkXiqA079kF9UPJ7Lge0MNNtKSwKMlyasFIUQenhDcvORVTPKh6JqbvXToLo9lzphx9dUXC_MzSZXQd-xdl0pmdNSmsm_SFkms8dvZZIbSFbRr7VrVJyvd3BW1UKmFYJQme_O5qHsPBTwd7mk8ccblRSR0bTcFT36j15V3Hwa2fFC7XI5r3wrJD0bG_]. The 'Let's Live Magnificently' global campaign (2023) aims to elevate everyday moments [https://www.fabnews.live/lets-live-magnificently-tanqueray-shakes-things-up-with-new-global-brand-campaign/, https://www.thedrum.com/news/2023/02/16/tanqueray-gin-unveils-first-global-campaign-5-years-after-moving-account-anomaly, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2023/02/tanqueray-unveils-global-campaign/]. The 'Fancy Hour' campaign (June 2024) focuses on martinis and elevated occasions [https://www.multivu.com/players/English/9270051-tanqueray-fancy-hour-martini-month/, https://sensational-sips.com/walking-the-talk-with-tanqueray/]. Diageo also increased marketing investment for Tanqueray, notably for its 'Unmistakably Tanqueray' campaign in 2021 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGT8Gt9aa25dGDamrwcCi_Q5MhwqtD1-7VWRKLtKR3vJuATkSPxFoD6DeocX12vKJFJ5K0VvtihRBKbF_PBvh-rY_jfFn3TNS0ue84AdyAlL_5MTsz3uDN4uXbBjKV7AJYxqCbsi__OLCJiJziUsJ2l-5U2XC2CeK0-DaQsvy5mcuvldB4uo4I, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFFh2qzQ20Uq5pDeuQJX8IKRaHyeg78JQyKWaQS2FmkG_mUnu15uuKdcBd3anz1qCHWyQM8elYQHd00vsWqJSxYzGIQ9kgUy1bZkz-XWCg96PR6T8Z-awkyXhOXddxDBeRhzjLeJXNtcq16i9qI_X4pAMrt4QUIUKDf-LYHL1eQ0tBgdZWZkdN6b_HvFCKQLN5b8ooJWR72ucGwd-MAhS09BJWJYdw=]. Tanqueray also engaged in celebrity partnerships with Stanley Tucci and Joe Jonas between 2021-2022 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGT8Gt9aa25dGDamrwcCi_Q5MhwqtD1-7VWRKLtKR3vJuATkSPxFoD6DeocX12vKJFJ5K0VvtihRBKbF_PBvh-rY_jfFn3TNS0ue84AdyAlL_5MTsz3uDN4uXbBjKV7AJYxqCbsi__OLCJiJziUsJ2l-5U2XC2CeK0-DaQsvy5mcuvldB4uo4I, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEmSol7tTnBwhubtRtfWjClBIvEiPW29jV-R1N8sSRKLaL_Ma53JwiHNa197rnzTBRAXCfAoTF1UHyvX959OUSypdW5vMgHbX4a76Kl9le2DKIghMjIAJOGT5ZXwjz66IxeepKW94HKMxr0zAzEcrApfyKceUvlVVsMRSVuDbtjpBJKVPMarke3LcV8lYsIWOoGxFfVJE5seAatY94oXPArJg==].\n*   **Influencer Marketing:** The partnership with Sarah Jessica Parker for the 'There's an N and an O in every ICON' campaign (January 2026) aims to leverage celebrity endorsement [https://www.designrush.com/news/tanqueray-sarah-jessica-parker-campaign, https://www.theginguild.com/tanqueray-announces-global-campaign-with-sarah-jessica-parker/, https://www.adsoftheworld.com/campaigns/300-nos]. This campaign aims to elevate Tanqueray's premium position and strengthen relevance in key markets including the UK, US, Brazil, China, India, and Italy [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGMYCp3y7wrj16jVwJvetBqvSxSvhgwiCuAenkS0KfWq5_nMygUPL7NLb7UOx8BmkTRXEVSoTuil0MxAOrnTxDASVk2qX70uUNMolTB92fdzkvVHQaE4BXdJdxSuELD6Rp3MW8tjAwzinq4C3na7dg7YFa2_ScF2w0kI8NfRGyvb88c4W6Y2e1q2BlxWbRekAEuQ==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFsXKeogblohNVw8F2bQXM7CBHbhEabkLoJxlVYD19-qbk-VMeYjzfzMn-Fa9wSdjfdhv6VUp1MsVLn0aMdudDqi_xfca9eope1CZVtE53UcetfuJp3Yeku18_9w-Bd-uwTNciLt2UcmKdQKyyK2G7A6ouBZYjW8r5cJplvL2SmsNPvv1z_jTStQfeKb03ScHyr0AIPFglZCI=]. However, the effectiveness and ROI of this partnership in reversing core volume decline and driving ongoing digital engagement are currently unclear due to its recent launch [https://www.diageo.com/news-media/news-releases/2026/sarah-jessica-parker-joins-tanqueray-as-global-ambassador, https://www.marketingweek.com/tanqueray-sarah-jessica-parker-partnership/]. There is a notable absence of comprehensive public analysis on the effectiveness and ROI of Tanqueray's recent marketing campaigns and celebrity partnerships, particularly in reversing core volume decline [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGlRuKeNrs_xlp61HPS-PwUp5qQlOPSwFckpz4qVdaIsE6tcpKj9LXJnCEdNYlPEb1vstg6ALUchRhqQdPF4C3uVOUIntxdN7bFKKgfN_rt2hwkn_481A8YLMLx_PtSvpxCbl9hiQn6UgUeHfw5-6rH5jKnOkzvuAddRS1cH5zMRAy9S3JtiJKOQ=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFaJpbM0f_b_0btdkDubcl61ux-810tS0QKLt0OlSzJrV7UtO5MVslQrqUaHEXRoGbIl55RUN408WwCo5Ouh1oY43fj8Gh43h6Laaf8qVyj3zHNvkOYrrYUmcM-ighPklku60vsoXNOikEAlZsSDU08rP2pgOXWnPY4i19TJLuc_xO3LIOjgc1gZ-KNbwGep-g6xwA=]. The effectiveness and ROI of Tanqueray's specific celebrity partnerships and marketing campaigns in reversing core volume decline and driving digital engagement remain largely unquantified in publicly available data from 2021-2025. While Diageo does not disclose granular ROI for traditional gin marketing, the company's non-alcoholic spirits portfolio, which includes Tanqueray 0.0, demonstrated significant growth of approximately **40% in fiscal 2025**, indicating a strategic focus on this segment [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHCwCy1yUlwOuYN7wLv8LBE0PsFgb2b_NL6AZf0dB9b3ayELi8SN1aVB7sstxJ_nBrZ1JDde3A_THnPCLjLXHLGYmXAG7sRaViEYFRxYCtt0XlJHfrHfi7S_wUOi1zvek7fu5ItT62tTEVkGpBcBtbJ9OieO1TMr2ZEvSWv, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGfyl68zSTlco3dtT8kTYMRVlbEBUXaYHWjAHYK4psfx-AaIvz6epcdrCN_AbH-9Xc4VOxEdRskVH3TSVliGqk22VtJ9fjp3BswD1sQGPKVhmQqO4x87iTbaP1TEE6lsuzu0DOHvPMcTcZsZXhW2UVckwMEkVwQLVNsmOcbzgIcMETvHxYV1Y4m8z-oyw==]. This suggests that while traditional marketing impact is opaque, investment in NoLo alternatives is yielding measurable results.\n*   **Distribution Optimization:** **[single-source]** Diageo planned a distribution overhaul in France by July 2024, recovering Tanqueray and Gordon's from the Moët Hennessy Diageo (MHD) joint venture [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE2aGOZzt1wzSKIBxKANbasUob1NXIDsM_NDB4CV0Db5OgLuVKLI1j_TsXJwIZTOJJXugpeJlQiPfpT89s_dLAB0T_6nl7dqebY51XDDcNXRnSdiJj2ufwrEWVgXrOeCii_utkmPos-n_xXbVBwwNbB16zv0xudmq-3Sowb].\n*   **Tariff/Duty Mitigation & Geopolitical Exposure:** The UK implemented a significant alcohol duty reform in August 2023, shifting taxation to an alcohol by volume (ABV) basis, resulting in an overall duty increase of 10.1% and heavier taxation for higher ABV products [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG25JG0ME2usmPVlS8j5YwWTiRaYQqXozn90tRiL87f6jpnULnr7dx0mUZ5sKt1ekPaabYZUcX7DHBrYKclXplN6tz9dnE-GOTwSlmfh8vYUTEr16TSY4ksRRlV8MHnEM04c-64IgqRhVwApJLsuHZL9xZGjEXB0GnUIueYh-QEfvAILW-eNv59RUxBRBfcI5o=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFQHKKELddCCOO2NQ6asadOuV1sboHpp_ev6nVSSiAA0C0zH7zP1rl_C4Bxj_I9sIs6Q7ds3JOdhDK1P7YBRzdszMgoFAZZhf7GA7fjxrnBP-1kOD0fLTJ8Z4jD3qwzgyb_, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHad-ER1Adlw9xxOUsf6fHX_pNajFVkxdfKOm2PLjfl9PB9pw4ULsSfpTDo1IqwPukY7armLHBiC9bxKdzHKeHAhJ3w4NuXfg6zCcellk2HO_kEq8hE-q64IuMdY2dl2D2GjyeH2bM_BpKtdH8MeSiFFTFJtDqv4NlebTWz2cBETzp60exhWDgv3wK30UKaWADr7chOSdRoTeC6ZUbnDLJ6Skkx0A_9feqDlU5g-UUCkhYQ_lbZGpH34LiZ8XfycBPgUt_WtspAxRoElNnbPSnJCw2WEEIzhCvgZitUfZ-Nj9i6jrelZGtYK41trKRvh109NBrKYephqL7mRIDRw8nLBDMmIgQTNg==]. In response, Tanqueray London Dry Gin specifically reduced its ABV from 43.1% to 41.3% in 2023 to mitigate these increased alcohol duties [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEQq_Ascr-KX79YEPV8k704lMuz4vuuYEZO594yCjdW_1THXemeHJO5-vvSSKyRA3uR_iOz-WZry4opPM2gvMq_q9gYAJI6_br8tEAYxATORsi62miHiGwsIYp2Vm84EqEv0_I1IBXLMpOMnKzqBzVkUQ4utJOz9gPMhPjD5zR-1g==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHaU17dgZVHscgSEZgpVivb_VuuKKnsYkayAuHeLFZejp4W7OR7dl1FfhXBWJi_Ndx3O66XKOMhHoNYYrfTrMYo7aOYANRGBI5IY6mRX67-dfRbdcrKy5Gd7xSh249nijglAVc6E53QLFwlRqeZX1iG-jmYIzlqihsWt8kzddnotdQBl1E4a06L3x5l5CRyJl-2, https://vertexaisearch.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG_HuIdsCtfx3HgNR5fYFplmtHCjAP1m1RMwe_R9nHvydicHCim7wvy9PvohdAtfCw8MuAH0jqaFL4cStdrowjKyWb1d0ifM2cwSW7nSiI4iCVhKMaikRZnM8HnsaM16zqlqhh87AFGs4MbnQHPEZ_enwjAxha4lVWFtU7dqD8=]. At its original ABV of 43.1%, the duty payable was £8.67, set to rise to £9.54. At the lowered 41.3% ABV, the duty was £8.31, escalating to £9.14 in August 2023 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEQq_Ascr-KX79YEPV8k704lMuz4vuuYEZO594yCjdW_1THXemeHJO5-vvSSKyRA3uR_iOz-WZry4opPM2gvMq_q9gYAJI6_br8tEAYxATORsi62miHiGwsIYp2Vm84EqEv0_I1IBXLMpOMnKzqBzVkUQ4utJOz9gPMhPjD5zR-1g==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHaU17dgZVHscgSEZgpVivb_VuuKKnsYkayAuHeLFZejp4W7OR7dl1FfhXBWJi_Ndx3O66XKOMhHoNYYrfTrMYo7aOYANRGBI5IY6mRX67-dfRbdcrKy5Gd7xSh249nijglAVc6E53QLFwlRqeZX1iG-jmYIzlqihsWt8kzddnotdQBl1E4a06L3x5l5CRyJl-2]. Further UK alcohol duty increases were anticipated and implemented from February 1, 2025, with non-draught products, including bottled spirits, expected to see duty rates rise in line with the Retail Price Index (RPI), estimated at 3.65% [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFgDs53yaSk0vlv9Ffn1SSr1xwukQXx4opxtvy6m9GrSqPjbhODFNO6jRVXHxCiFo00b-InXvzvjeNjXk5eHyWqp9FJe18AEi63c_Wid5GEihjRi9s_hsL4edXFN9V-gFvMG8XX6HjNfVsugW96838=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEuJrRAGTsiKFhNJ9jLhd7RUKMCcORbiDvYqkC3yNEoejkCWv_o4_htDNlVdr49KdKvPmmtnx8oDndlOly_A-VaomJlNHwydALz9--k-KRa7ocRc7wjX0wfq4jQXRtOZ0n2EivBEZ8vIcYjIV_qowQVXCLDNYTqe58Bko5_gA90k-oFfeuUVP5_jwXuRKCT9E4vuOSjDUveHdb7RWfSkg==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH_SWly_kTXXM7NAIDStyzx4s5rp9RruTt51tbYOYMe4rM-fMNCCJ9o9TkhHr4ON2N4Maflu-k0eauVuHxobBUx7bDTXFqXWrDtm3q8ifH9x_mdEbjvKiiXbAnHp-e9A8XTe7UBVL4yJUJCm7LYj-ktgBxNGlNktyW2na9O3uvsWRKO3TFiTMRBTz4iOg==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHoU6InvuCczKQkOqVYL8eQFrUlUpVrcILLUsjXHfOQp6gJmMywMh5aJ6m7g65PMh_Wo3doIn8rN5HWBhn8cw7eHPgZtpLYyegcC-4OmXKr7wfq1sTbRzAp7Juxtrw4pf2L5yf8OsbQkg7d1Sh5gfkBdh756utt1TNnSp-vYr16zmnlPiMq, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFKG1qh_a3I57hbYI5JGVZl7vvXyqPnFZiHSuxkZ7eBxxyzbpEad9t98C7xnv88GBTNcxy4WoPMJcBsFzAENFtpsy15Br5iWhCvctvIfbR--ePXirvsxC83C7PAvVSaLso25r-blPl4w8w9thHVPEBJ0refIJL9T0lQEA==]. For spirits, the duty on a 70cl bottle of 40% ABV alcohol increased by 33p from February 1, 2025 [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHoU6InvuCczKQkOqVYL8eQFrUlUpVrcILLUsjXHfOQp6gJmMywMh5aJ6m7g65PMh_Wo3doIn8rN5HWBhn8cw7eHPgZtpLYyegcC-4OmXKr7wfq1sTbRzAp7Juxtrw4pf2L5yf8OsbQkg7d1Sh5gfkBdh756utt1TNnSp-vYr16zmnlPiMq, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFKG1qh_a3I57hbYI5JGVZl7vvXyqPnFZiHSuxkZ7eBxxyzbpEad9t98C7xnv88GBTNcxy4WoPMJcBsFzAENFtpsy15Br5iWhCvctvIfbR--ePXirvsxC83C7PAvVSaLso25r-blPl4w8w9thHVPEBJ0refIJL9T0lQEA==]. This highlights a clear geopolitical and regulatory sensitivity, impacting product formulation and pricing strategies [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFDDeWBU6exAPibBm946m2VdJJo4HKbQbN8Q1R7ywKv2L_1021cXvHXQAk6pGekEohj0gGSaB470yJf3yRMC10veosAWX0XUMNLiYyuo2ECyqdZISxSMQ7ptn-3b_QZfH3SzdyOCPjFns5ixdAPiYraNz-7c4Q5sm4QkP5of, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGPVw19Rkk_9HOqMYgNp_zs_PIUrFWlFwr29GNEl6HW7y6UEAp-OS9o9Y2vUZniJpkxv29EifrG8jhucJehwy4cJE2BXjQeNk0OLoYWJ3spWS4sCrFA1IWEPGcwotxmJLmAVSRKhhN6fsbSnO1q]. Beyond UK-specific duties, Diageo anticipated an annual financial impact of **$150 million to $200 million from US tariffs on UK and European spirits imports in 2025** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEngE_IadEDZyNjztizZJ9I_GnO7l6XrHceQAb04j7tbyzZhwvTZxG-THl-SAEotvasGJjltk6ntAY9MYkUTWgeXZv9BOY_HikbLJ6NA1JSJK-aCdDKLFERnZDRJkQEnTpw3quiyLPlmfOWJ2kLN9JsF-srDqjwiQsaSC67fEPJ48iFVxJdjlKLTlpvoEqItcHcB22JGPmQ, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEcVjzt8KOBrr-dpFrjrpSKzcUqj48XhAZC-3gwx_8N1Vm3hqk_o_sG900MoAmk7_YXrP8xR-DlOYAAd9gvh5LVmvrVtPFByb4kcGiosG8IXKg8jzk5w2_2bMspvxQUP8FkpRRY07p0sKYpzY0rB_v5ZzXbLxfQzVYZDTu0i41A3VFnDrAMdks6evJC4Bn9ex13GYvXQc0RRrqrY0Y, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFWDpihKxlHlBzEum7rLiIhR3ldxbQVJZhfhuMVbYnjElK05rpdIgVCQY206z2O0KyEaRsKs-nI41uyRGpU10BCOqH_Uk7yuz6dvHPMdLWNz57T5-wWtAnYVLqgR-uttKtPT9sh-OKVDwvKIj82glLdFGh3plrw71G339DFIwU0e6L_TTrj7c-AEfHcc]. Diageo expected to mitigate about half of this impact through various strategies, including expanding its cost-cutting plan from **£500 million to £625 million (or €444 million to $500 million)** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEcVjzt8KOBrr-dpFrjrpSKzcUqj48XhAZC-3gwx_8N1Vm3hqk_o_sG900MoAmk7_YXrP8xR-DlOYAd9gvh5LVmvrVtPFByb4kcGiosG8IXKg8jzk5w2_2bMspvxQUP8FkpRRY07p0sKYpzY0rB_v5ZzXbLxfQzVYZDTu0i41A3VFnDrAMdks6evJC4Bn9ex13GYvXQc0RRrqrY0Y, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFj76Pn42xt-kg07mFQPQahqv7XENI7LmkKtqepsaAK_rqnfvk_fhkrZx--xj15ODQlPO4NxhCRsLEocFt-ktcAzfbc59nhNaaTpG4gUkorH5vC83V64vy--kHazG90Ja6bsn85fSuM8DoD9wl4mZ0qkY_0cnuDY5w0t2h9BBqPQw_uId0UiZCmI4ovtCIfHRoIdUGl6vACRSsoSn6GTEo]. Diageo's geopolitical tariff mitigation strategies include cost absorption, supply chain optimization (inventory management, reallocation of investments), and a US$500 million cost-saving program over three years [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHblJY0fuT6jkhaSr2j3R7js0bjaNEl6Xf5Tc7OXFD5wgDBNVkDr-DV2xNCfl4t-bF0hE6lgj7HHyd4LxEkmo84V98C77vRIzwXwS_b7TOmVvan2Svjm4Cm9nU3AfBqjb-XsujdXen3OqTCFy4b4OCRnxkkpS-ZBVd8D4YgI8hvANfBdB0jfjXmK45rqWo=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEBFENSjHce3CtJfZBYDa9oKdtaHWZ0N_o-kDDy0z0q-e5wXkH7dmHpxk0n25KP_Rn17xj1AXY0whriGdk4WY_Pm8dPqSDRQHHUy5PaF6qcA2HmwAHNcZpytYs7ZT6M27T2aEADwW69Hgw9mTt9BvYvOH5r9S3rTo72zUKCOnh6suXZZDhVluJArEvcOc3ilCYVfkAPp198Tec0r2GElU11pVqJ4g-i6fQ==, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGwyoNCWSHTjPle5uN2lqF5143FJK1_36p4Iu9v_zL8YOoA7wPg0ZmfjXaQxkT_nvWnH8wGXQYX2p3Mdr79cT9LV3TBkVQ70JXMjZFxmnP01FDPd-4eRCXP]. Trade tensions also affect the cost and availability of raw materials like glass and cork [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHtlslHTf-DBxGC28AxKFa0vuHbv70qsbj0efg6xeOKUeUA440IUXoaxAKPPj0wMSNmD5nK750thvadw2gY_kbz5R8H9OA-eRJlvrg8dVqy--Dho5o-AeEeCtnALoT1d6fBsBqCYMCtLq1biLqIm8Mjk8Tib-quIb7QJwRwtV86, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEZcteFiu_YO1ZfTstv1sMTnDSTC_k6vWwOC8hynC4tjWjNJu0SDiHLtUigKgpKOjpfnxvKRDestd91lTZOHKdlsvLTZAxXtV34WC_yGU6tKxArAwCetEEEPIN3HigECMDoA_wzzaFU3jRzttMj2L9fuwSmcdi2uUOpCv1TYJ2rktTw3FcVBCrez_yJ86vqIx2O-dcE]. Diageo's CFO also stated that potential US tariffs on Canada and Mexico could cost the business **$200 million in gross exposure on operating profit**, with 85% largely on tequila [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFtkTEt4sfV1GtFmN4EzCkO9G-TtBJeI33JusfnkDM1NbfDlszzHJcBLV8R1iFvT7qVoyib8ewn8Gnjyz1VeHKrq3WF-DLnK1Ekz93A41JC427tJ2DkrL3OGWN-9rJX0n9i35dyLbVzt_FiLIySUnDLyCve5hsPgrXxLyrut2Maa1Jlx16R8afGDbYasFsXPRO26JSI3vDXyLdHf0oWncqzQUDPNNMCUzi9aNs_TUA1MDaYHhxFHvf5PnA6SA]. US tariffs on UK distilled spirits and wines are set to \"snap back\" on **July 4, 2026**, and on EU spirits and wines on **July 11, 2026**, if no trade agreements are reached [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHblJY0fuT6jkhaSr2j3R7js0bjaNEl6Xf5Tc7OXFD5wgDBNVkDr-DV2xNCfl4t-bF0hE6lgj7HHyd4LxEkmo84V98C77vRIzwXwS_b7TOmVvan2Svjm4Cm9nU3AfBqjb-XsujdXen3OqTCFy4b4OCRnxkkpS-ZBVd8D4YgI8hvANfBdB0jfjXmK45rqWo=, https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEBFENSjHce3CtJfZBYDa9oKdtaHWZ0N_o-kDDy0z0q-e5wXkH7dmHpxk0n25KP_Rn17xj1AXY0whriGdk4WY_Pm8dPqSDRQHHUy5PaF6qcA2HmwAHNcZpytYs7ZT6M27T2aEADwW69Hgw9mTt9BvYvOH5r9S3rTo72zUKCOnh6suXZZDhVluJArEvcOc3ilCYVfkAPp198Tec0r2GElU11pVqJ4g-i6fQ==]. While Diageo has provided estimates for the financial impact of US tariffs on its overall spirits imports (ranging from US$150 million to US$200 million annually), a specific, quantified financial impact on Tanqueray's individual profitability due to these tariffs or UK duty changes is not publicly detailed. The available data focuses on the broader company-wide impact rather than brand-specific figures [https://www.diageo.com/news-and-media/press-releases/diageo-reports-half-year-fiscal-2021-results, https://www.thespiritsbusiness.com/2021/01/diageo-half-year-sales-fall-8-due-to-covid-19-and-tariffs/]. The specific, quantified financial impact of geopolitical tariff impacts on Tanqueray's profitability is not publicly detailed by Diageo [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF-3qwaWO_PoG6wQKPOJZRu3nt0H5vjbafT6muHWb3mEH1LvcvPU1g0Eu6UTYxzJGSNnzqVj2bzBfAp-YULds8yxy8mRCJTqQVqTk9kr1PO5QAZLokO4Gfo8LVpVNs6aVR-D6Z1sA6P4sXe0FnLYh-yCfvcKHxjl3HX].\n\n"},{"level":3,"title":"7. Performance","content":"\n*   **Global Volume Trends:**\n    *   **2019:** Tanqueray's organic net sales grew by **19%** [https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHCwCy1yUlwOuYN7wLv8LBE0PsFgb2b_NL6AZf0dB9b3ayELi8SN1aVB7sstxJ_nBrZ1JDde3A_THnPCLjLXHLGYmXAG7sRaViEYFRxYC\n"}]
